Chicago Man Found Guilty of Aiding Planners of 2008 Mumbai Terror Attacks

-- B y   A n d r e w   H a r r i s
-- 
2011-06-09T21:36:57Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-09/chicago-man-found-guilty-of-aiding-planners-of-2008-mumbai-terror-attacks.html
A  Chicago  man accused of helping
planners of the 2008 Mumbai terrorist attacks that killed about
160 people including six Americans was found guilty by a federal
jury in Chicago.  To contact the reporter on this story:
